author: gbrown
msg: Update FlowPane preferred size calculations to account for baseline alignment; fix some minor memory leaks in various decorators; add a BaselineDecorator class to assist in debugging baseline code (the previous approach, which used a drawBaselineDebug() method in ComponentSkin, did not work for container skins, whose children are painted over their contents).
